  -- See also Modality.Left-exact.η-[]◯-η≃◯.

  ◯→η-[]◯-η : ◯ (x < y) → η x [ _<_ ]◯ η y
  ◯→η-[]◯-η = ◯-map (λ x<y → _ , _ , refl _ , refl _ , x<y)

  -- If A is modal and _<_ has type A → A → Type a, then
  -- η x [ _<_ ]◯ η y is equivalent to ◯ (x < y).
